          </p>
          <p class="font-body text-brand-stone text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Trabajamos con guías locales certificados y colaboradores de confianza para garantizarte
            autenticidad, seguridad y momentos únicos. Solo tienes que decirnos qué te apetece y
            nuestro equipo lo organiza todo: recogida, reservas y hasta la cesta de picnic para el
            camino.
          </p>

        </div>

        <!-- Right: 2×2 image mosaic -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">

          <!-- REPLACE: real photo -->
          <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
            <img
              src="/assets/images/sierra-tower-wide.jpg"
              alt="Senderismo en la Sierra de Irta"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
            />
          </div>

          <!-- REPLACE: real photo -->
          <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
            <img
              src="/assets/images/sierra-tower-sea.jpg"
              alt="Kayak en el Mediterráneo"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
            />
          </div>

          <!-- REPLACE: real photo -->
          <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
            <img
              src="/assets/images/sierra-trail-vertical.jpg"
              alt="Castillo de Peñíscola"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
            />
          </div>

          <!-- REPLACE: real photo -->
          <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl">
            <img
              src="/assets/images/property-aerial-pool.jpg"
              alt="Gastronomía local — arroz a banda"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
            />
          </div>

        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ============================================================
       SECTION 2b: NUESTROS PAQUETES (dynamic — Hi.Events)
       3-column card grid. UPCOMING → full card + Reservar CTA.
       PAST/ENDED → desaturated + "Finalizado" badge, no CTA.
       Empty state → elegant placeholder copy.
       ============================================================ -->
  <section
    id="paquetes"
    class="bg-[#EEF4E6] py-24 md:py-32 px-4"
    aria-label="Nuestros paquetes de experiencias"
  >
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">

      <!-- TODO: REMOVE BEFORE LAUNCH — beta disclaimer -->
      <div class="mb-10 bg-amber-400/90 border border-amber-300 text-amber-950 font-body text-sm px-4 py-3 rounded-lg text-center">
        ⚠️ Sistema en fase de pruebas. Para reservas, contacta directamente por teléfono:
        <a href="tel:+34644026066" class="font-semibold underline">+34 644 026 066</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Section header -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 text-center mb-16">
        <p class="font-body uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-brand-gold text-xs font-medium">
          RESERVA TU EXPERIENCIA
        </p>
        <h2 class="font-display font-light text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl text-brand-blue leading-tight">
          Nuestros Paquetes
        </h2>
